<h2>Hello <%=@user.mail%></h2>

<% if @user.token_reset? %>
	Your token was reset! The previous token was inactivated
<% end %>

<p>
	Your token is <%=@user.token%>
</p>

<p>
	You can use the same token as many times as you want
</p>

<p>
	If you didn't request this token, just ignore this mail
</p>

<p>
	If you have any doubts or suggestions, please leave a message at <a href="http://pablocantero.com/blog/contato/">http://pablocantero.com/blog/contato/</a>
</p>

